## Repository Structure

This is a multi-project repository containing the following subprojects:

- **apitable/** — APITable (spreadsheet/database platform)
- **collabspace/** — CollabSpace (collaboration platform)
- **lottery/** — Lottery application
- **mattermost/** — Mattermost (messaging/communication platform)

Each subdirectory is intended to hold an independent project. As of initial setup, these directories are empty placeholders awaiting code.

## Development Notes

- IDE: JetBrains (`.idea/` config present)
- Not a git repository at the top level; individual subprojects may have their own version control


